## 2 · REPO ARCHITECTURE

```
Portfolio/
├── index.html                          # Main portfolio page (~1843 lines)
├── styles.css                          # Glassmorphism design system (~1377 lines)
├── script.js                           # Scroll animations, typewriter, promo code
├── [company]-[feature]-prototype.html  # ~60+ standalone prototype files
├── assets/
│   ├── build-[company]-[feature]-deck.js  # PptxGenJS build scripts
│   └── [company]-[feature]-deck.pptx      # Generated CEO decks
├── .claude/commands/apply.md           # Self-evolving workflow skill
├── CLAUDE.md                           # Claude Code rules
├── .clinerules                         # Roo-Code/Cline agent rules (this file)
├── .cursorrules                        # Cursor agent rules
├── package.json                        # http-server + pptxgenjs
└── vercel.json                         # Static hosting config
```

**No build step.** Plain HTML/CSS/JS. Serve with `npm start` (port 3000).

