## 3 · WORKFLOW — 6 PHASES (Never Skip Any)

```
Phase 1 → Parse JD → Brainstorm 3–5 case studies → Get Ajay's input → Confirm brief
Phase 2 → Build HTML prototype (4 screens) → QA checklist
Phase 3 → Build PptxGenJS CEO deck (8 slides) → Text extraction QA
Phase 4 → Add portfolio block to index.html → git push → Update case studies table
Phase 5 → Generate HTML resume → Self-check → Generate PDF via Chrome Headless
Phase 6 → Write LinkedIn note (≤300 chars) + email in .txt format → QA
```

**Rule: Always confirm the case study direction (Phase 1.4 brief) before building anything.**

