## 4 · PROTOTYPE TEMPLATE (Phase 2)

### 4.1 File Convention
`/Users/ajayavaghade/Portfolio/[company-slug]-[feature]-prototype.html`

All prototypes are fully self-contained — single HTML file, no external JS (except Google Fonts).

### 4.2 Best Reference Sample
**`adyen-smartcheckout-prototype.html`** — has both phone + browser frames, full tab-switching navigation, annotation panel, confetti.

### 4.3 Two Frame Types

| Type | Width | Use When |
|------|-------|----------|
| Phone Frame | 375px, border-radius 46px | Consumer-facing features (app screens) |
| Browser Frame | 640px, browser chrome | Dashboards, ops tools, admin panels |

### 4.4 Skeleton Template

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
