## 13 · QUICK START FOR NEW JD

```
1. Read the agent rules (.clinerules / .cursorrules) — you now have full context
2. Parse the JD → Extract role, priorities, keywords, gaps, location
3. Brainstorm 3-5 case studies → Present to Ajay → Get sign-off
4. Build prototype using Section 4 template → QA with Section 4.11
5. Build CEO deck using Section 5 template → QA with Section 5.7
6. Add portfolio block using Section 6.1 template → git push
7. Generate resume using Section 7 template → QA with Section 7.5
8. Write outreach using Section 8 templates → QA
9. Update Section 10 table + Evolution Log in apply.md
```

**Estimated effort per run:** 45–90 minutes. Prototype is the longest phase.

**Deliverables per run:** 1 prototype HTML, 1 PPTX deck, 1 HTML resume, 1 LinkedIn note, 1 email.
